        protected FC getFrameConversion(IFrame frame)
        Provides a conversion of the specified frame, including any required structure representing frame-type and/or slots. The provided conversion will be a previously created entity if this method has already been invoked for the specified frame. Otherwise it will be newly created and configured.
        Parameters:
        frame - Frame whose conversion is required
        Returns:
        Converted and configured frame
